  "lyrics": "Yeah, I see you when you're standin' there The left side of my dreams tonight What does it mean to you? One touch from you will send me beyond the sky Just thinkin' about it brings a doom to my mind Once you do that, once you feel it You can't go back, can't go back Yeah, once you pass that line between all right and wrong Gotta get it through All this catchin' it, all this smilin' it All the feeling makin' this alive Every second for your sake You go past it, you die, we'll find you But there's times when you know the night gets harder You'll be a fighter You want more than you can eat Right, so you just try and survive it Won't go past the line, you know that Can't go back, can't go back Yeah, once you take it, once you know how you make that decision It has all you know Oh, I wish you wasn't so young You know that thoughts are meant to heal And you can't go back, can't go back No matter what you think, you hear the promise, you're wrong Have all your decisions, your decisions, your consequences Be there what you see and is it really you inside the dream?",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 5.78000020980835,
      "text": "Yeah, I see you when you're standin' there",
      "start": 0
    },
    {
      "end": 12.9399995803833,
      "text": "The left side of my dreams tonight",
      "start": 7.019999980926514
    },
    {
      "end": 16.059999465942383,
      "text": "What does it mean to you?",
      "start": 14
    },
    {
      "end": 19.860000610351562,
      "text": "One touch from you will send me beyond the sky",
      "start": 16.31999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 28,
      "text": "Just thinkin' about it brings a doom to my mind",
      "start": 23
    },
    {
      "end": 32.540000915527344,
      "text": "Once you do that, once you feel it",
      "start": 29
    },
    {
      "end": 36.380001068115234,
      "text": "You can't go back, can't go back",
      "start": 32.540000915527344
    },
    {
      "end": 42.97999954223633,
      "text": "Yeah, once you pass that line between all right and wrong",
      "start": 36.380001068115234
    },
    {
      "end": 44.380001068115234,
      "text": "Gotta get it through",
      "start": 42.97999954223633
    },
    {
      "end": 48.18000030517578,
      "text": "All this catchin' it, all this smilin' it",
      "start": 44.380001068115234
    },
    {
      "end": 50,
      "text": "All the feeling makin' this alive",
      "start": 48.18000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 52.7599983215332,
      "text": "Every second for your sake",
      "start": 50.599998474121094
    },
    {
      "end": 59.20000076293945,
      "text": "You go past it, you die, we'll find you",
      "start": 54.31999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 64.81999969482422,
      "text": "But there's times when you know the night gets harder",
      "start": 59.20000076293945
    },
    {
      "end": 66.68000030517578,
      "text": "You'll be a fighter",
      "start": 64.91999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 70.95999908447266,
      "text": "You want more than you can eat",
      "start": 67.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 74.91999816894531,
      "text": "Right, so you just try and survive it",
      "start": 70.95999908447266
    },
    {
      "end": 78.5,
      "text": "Won't go past the line, you know that",
      "start": 74.91999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 82.0199966430664,
      "text": "Can't go back, can't go back",
      "start": 78.5
    },
    {
      "end": 86.77999877929688,
      "text": "Yeah, once you take it, once you know how you make that decision",
      "start": 82.0199966430664
    },
    {
      "end": 89.73999786376953,
      "text": "It has all you know",
      "start": 87.18000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 93.91999816894531,
      "text": "Oh, I wish you wasn't so young",
      "start": 90.41999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 96.23999786376953,
      "text": "You know that thoughts are meant to heal",
      "start": 93.91999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 99.66000366210938,
      "text": "And you can't go back, can't go back",
      "start": 96.23999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 105.16000366210938,
      "text": "No matter what you think, you hear the promise, you're wrong",
      "start": 99.66000366210938
